it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.dagjgrapht

Class Intersection<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.dagjgrapht.Intersection<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - BasicClassDescription or Property

    public class Intersection<T>
extends Object
    Represents intersections of classes or properties as all the sub-classes (resp., sub-properties). Such a representation makes containment checks fast.
    Author:
    Roman Kontchakov
